</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>This news just in from <a href="http://blog.springsource.com/author/arjenp/">Arjen Poutsma</a>'s <a href="https://twitter.com/poutsma">twitter feed</a>: Spring 3.0.0.RC1 is now available.</p>
<p><br><br></p>
